The paper deals with face recognition using deep convolutional neural networks, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The use of neural networks also suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of neural networks (cs.NE), machine learning (cs.LG), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the organization of face space and the perception of caricatures, which could relate to human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
